Bad channels:
  - Are set through raw plot
  - Are kept in epoch collection creation
  - Are kept in evoked collection creation, but excluded in plotting / saving
  - Are excluded in spectrum creation
  - are excluded in tfr creation

Channel name cleaning:
  - Currently channel averaging cleans names by removing whitespace, no side effects
  - In spectrums and TFR's, group average cleans names by removing whitespace, has side effect that group average item has cleaned channel names
  - In spectrums, plot_spectrum_topo cleans names, has no side effects
